# resolve(in:)

**Instance Method**

Resolves the associated value in the given coordinate space.

## Declaration

```swift
func resolve<Space>(in otherSpace: Space) throws -> Self.Value where Space : CoordinateSpace3D
```

## Return Value

A concrete value converted to the provided space.
